#Test scripts for sample app
#Only for reference, the test scripts are based on demo app.

Sample Test scripts for:
-To verify if the search results match the exact query string
-To verify if filter works correctly

------------------------------------------------------

Pre-Requisite:
-Python 2.7
-Firefox browser

-----------------------------------------------------

Setup:
-Install python 
$sudo yum install python

-Install selenium
$sudo yum install python-pip
$pip-python install -U selenium

---------------------------------------------------------

Config File Attributes:
Change the config.conf.sample to config.conf and set the required options.
- Define the URL in which the test case should run
- Define the Path to set up Reports & log Folders

---------------------------------------------------------

Step to execute the script:
1. To run the test suite:
./main.py --all

2. To run a test case:
./main.py -t filter_case
./main.py -t search_case

*Reports generated on test run are contained in the folder 'reports/' in the user specified location.

